# Usage

## Installation

Add `{:ice_cream, "~> 0.0.4"}` to your list of dependencies

```elixir
Mix.install([{:ice_cream, "~> 0.0.4"}])
```

## Usage

In your module, add `use IceCream` then just use `ic/0` or `ic/2`!

```elixir
defmodule Foo do
  use IceCream

  def bar(baz) do
    ic(baz)
  end
end

Foo.bar("a string")
```
